data.description: SELLING AS IS! Needs painting inside and out. Carpet has been removed, so can not go FHA or VA. It is structually sound just needs to be pruced up again. Master Bedroom is down stairs with huge walk in closet.  2nd living area upstairs could be used  for workout equipment or a game room. There is a Mullberry tree out back that is producing. Home has lots of potenial. Great location in Chapel Hill. There is  a little park across the street with sitting area. The Pool and Playground a walking distance away only a couple of blocks. New High School is being built less then 2 miles away. Great location not far from main highways and shopping.
